column2: SELECT   m.ra_#, m.dec_#, m.specObjID, S.ra, S.dec, S.specObjID,   S.mjd, S.plate, S.fiberID, S.class,   S.z, S.zErr, S.rChi2, S.velDisp, S.velDispErr, dbo.fgeturlfitsspectrum(S.specobjid),   G.extinction_r,   G.modelMag_u, G.modelMagErr_u, G.modelMag_g, G.modelMagErr_g,   G.modelMag_r, G.modelMagErr_r, G.modelMag_i, G.modelMagErr_i,   G.modelMag_z, G.modelMagErr_z,   GSL.oii_#_flux, GSL.oii_#_flux_err,    GSL.neiii_#_flux, GSL.neiii_#_flux_err,   GSL.h_gamma_flux, GSL.h_gamma_flux_err,   GSL.nii_#_flux, GSL.nii_#_flux_err,    GSL.h_alpha_flux, GSL.h_alpha_flux_err,    GSL.oiii_#_flux, GSL.oiii_#_flux_err,   GSL.h_beta_flux, GSL.h_beta_flux_err,    GSL.h_delta_flux, GSL.h_delta_flux_err,    GSL.sii_#_flux, GSL.sii_#_flux_err,   GSL.sii_#_flux, GSL.sii_#_flux_err,     GSX.d4#, GSX.d4#_err   INTO MyDB.chandra_matched_sdss_details1# FROM MyDB.chandra_matched_sdss_# AS m     OUTER APPLY dbo.fGetNearestObjEQ(m.ra_#, m.dec_#, #) AS n, specObj AS S     WHERE n.ObjID=S.bestObjID     JOIN SpecPhoto AS G, GalSpecLine AS GSL, GalSpecIndx AS GSX     WHERE S.specObjID = G.specObjID     AND S.specObjID = GSL.specObjID     AND S.specObjID = GSX.specObjID
